name: 20 Years of SF Dance Music DOSC Audio NFT
description: Nearly everyone who has regularly gone out in San Francisco over the last twenty years has seen, heard, and been moved by waves of change in some ways very different from all the others that came before. 5 top SF DJs and Musicians are combining forces for a collective ensemble release with DIGIFIZZY. Taking those tunes to the digi base. Hailing from San Francisco, Dosc (Jason Urbina) is creating his artistic foothold in the dance music industry by blending genre-specific sounds to produce tracks that unite divisions of music.
